    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Þráinn Ashward is the Pale Maw Inquisitor commanding the cult's operations in Svellheim — tall, gaunt, one eye scarred across and unhidden, dressed in deep purple robes with silver entropy symbols. He is analytical, certain, and merciless. His Zealot's Judgment marks targets for follow-up devastation, and his Voice of Entropy can terrify entire clusters of heroes simultaneously. His Despair Aura degrades enemy effectiveness while bolstering his own cultists. He cannot be bargained with, only stopped.</p>",
